name: Personalized AI Storybooks
description: Apps that generate personalized, multimodal children's stories and illustrated books—turning photos, doodles, or pets into consistent characters with AI images, narration, animation, and interactive educational features.

name: AI Visual Storytelling
description: Projects that use multimodal AI to generate, transform, and personalize images and narratives—turning audio, text, and data into accessible visual stories, educational guides, and personalized art for diverse users.

name: AI Visual Learning Tools
description: Projects build AI-driven visual and interactive educational tools using Gemini/Nano Banana to generate consistent characters, mnemonic images, comics, slides, and personalized avatars that make learning engaging and multimodal across subjects.

name: Generative Geospatial Visuals
description: Projects use multimodal AI to generate and transform maps, temporal scenes, and natural imagery—enabling interactive geospatial visualizations, climate/time simulations, creative alternate worlds, and plant/crop diagnosis tools.

name: Personalized AI Avatars
description: Apps that transform user photos into consistent AI-driven characters and avatars for personalized, interactive narratives, games, dream visualizations, and virtual companions using multimodal image-and-text generation.

name: AI Manga Studio
description: Tools that convert story prompts into consistent multi-panel manga and comics using advanced image-generation models, automating storyboarding, character consistency, and page orchestration for rapid, publishable sequential art.

name: AI Comic Generation
description: Tools that use advanced multimodal AI (Gemini/Nano Banana) to convert text, images, and dialogue into consistent, multi-panel comics, webtoons, and storyboards with character continuity, personalization, and rapid automated styling.

name: Generative Visual Asset Tools
description: AI-powered tools for generating, editing, and organizing visual assets—spritesheets, character concepts, isometric worlds, fused images, and video prompts—streamline creative workflows for game and media production.

name: Generative Video Studio
description: Automated tools that convert stories, text, images, or wireframes into consistent multi‑scene visuals, storyboards, animations, and short-form videos with synchronized voice, music, and effects using Gemini, Nano Banana, Veo, and ElevenLabs.

name: AI Visual Storytelling
description: Tools that convert scripts, prompts, or images into consistent, cinematic storyboards, animations, and short films using multimodal AI for character fidelity, frame-by-frame editing, and automated production pipelines.

name: Multimodal AI Storytelling
description: Multimodal AI tools that transform text prompts into consistent illustrated, narrated, and animated comics or videos, enabling interactive, real-time, and exportable storytelling with character continuity.

name: AI Virtual Fashion Studio
description: AI tools that generate photorealistic product and on-model imagery, virtual try-on, and image-based shopping to replace photoshoots and simplify fashion e-commerce content creation and discovery.

name: AI Virtual Try-On
description: AI-powered virtual try-on projects using multimodal image editing to let users instantly visualize clothing, accessories, and outfits on themselves and in spaces, enabling personalized shopping, browser integrations, and reduced purchase uncertainty.

name: Virtual Style Try-On
description: AI-powered photorealistic virtual try-on tools that let users preview and experiment with hairstyles, beards, nails, tattoos, and other personal style changes on their own photos before committing.

name: AI Virtual Wardrobe
description: AI-powered virtual wardrobe and styling tools that let users digitize closets, get personalized outfit recommendations, and perform realistic virtual try-ons and color/style analyses for planning, shopping, and occasions.

name: AI Food Imaging and Recipes
description: AI apps that analyze food photos to generate personalized recipes, meal plans, nutrition insights, and professional-quality dish visuals for cooking guidance, menu previews, and reduced food waste.

name: AI Sticker & Emoji Tools
description: Collection of AI-powered tools that convert photos and graphics into personalized stickers, emojis, avatars, and branded sticker packs with emotion transforms, QR-code integration, and one-click exports.

name: Personalized AI Photo Studio
description: Projects that use generative multimodal AI to transform, edit, anonymize, and stylize user photos—from professional headshots and cultural portraits to celebrity photobombs, age-progression, group compositing, and pose editing.

name: Photo Restoration and Reimagining
description: A set of AI-powered tools to restore, colorize, and repair photos and artworks, plus era-aware style transfers, atmospheric edits, and creative reimagining that reconstructs and time-travels images for personal and historical use.

name: Personal AI Visualizations
description: AI-generated personalized visuals for self-reflection, memory, identity, and motivation—transforming photos, dreams, and feelings into art, timelines, tarot, and future-self media to support creativity, emotional insight, and behavior change.

name: Personalized Photo Memories
description: Tools that use multimodal generative AI to create personalized, identity-consistent photos, albums, and memorial portraits—placing people into travel scenes, events, or keepsake formats to preserve and share memories.

name: AI Image Stylization
description: A collection of Gemini-powered apps that generate and stylize user images into themed visual assets—portraits, posters, covers, memes, and synthetic datasets—enabling fast, consistent, and personalized content creation.

name: AI Image Editing Tools
description: A collection of projects that use multimodal generative AI to edit, enhance, and create images and visualizers from photos, text, audio, and poems via natural-language and semantic controls.

name: AI Visual Content Studio
description: AI-powered tools using Google's Nano Banana/Gemini models to generate consistent, branded marketing visuals, product mockups, relighting, and stylized creative assets for fast, automated content and presentation creation.

name: Nano Banana 3D Views
description: Projects using Nano Banana to generate consistent multi-angle images, orthographic views, and point-cloud/3D outputs from single or few 2D inputs for interactive product views, 3D model creation, prints, and visual simulations.

name: AI Visual Design Tools
description: Tools that use multimodal AI to convert text, sketches, photos, and diagrams into polished visuals—mockups, step-by-step instructions, technical diagrams, and scientific or exhibit illustrations—enabling rapid design, repair guides, and prototyping.

name: Interactive AI Image Tools
description: A suite of multimodal AI tools for interactive, branching, and collaborative image generation, editing, enhancement, and forensic analysis that enable real-time co-creation, tile-based canvases, and programmable visual workflows.

name: Nano Banana Image Tools
description: Projects building Nano Banana/Gemini-powered multimodal image generation and editing tools—canvas and node editors, mobile apps, plugins, version control, and prompt agents—for region-aware, iterative, and consistent creative image workflows.

name: Interactive Visual AI
description: Image-centric AI apps that generate, edit, and analyze visuals—combined with voice—to power interactive games, spot-the-difference puzzles, home/insurance inspections, emergency response, and safety/fraud prevention.

name: AI Image Editing Suite
description: A suite of AI-powered image generation and editing tools—canvas apps, voice and sketch interfaces, collaborative editors, and asset generators (textures, shaders)—enabling rapid creative composition and photorealistic manipulations using Gemini/Nano Banana models.

name: AI Architectural Visualization
description: AI-driven tools that convert sketches, photos, and blueprints into photorealistic architectural visualizations, 3D models, walkthroughs, and urban-planning scenarios with iterative editing and contextual consistency.

name: AI Interior Visualization
description: Tools that use multimodal generative AI to transform photos of rooms, homes, and exteriors into photorealistic redesigns, virtual staging, moodboards, 3D visualizations, and product try‑ons to help users plan, shop, and market spaces.

name: AI Product Imagery
description: Tools that use multimodal AI to generate, enhance, and contextualize product images and 3D models for e-commerce, enabling studio-quality photos, mockups, virtual try-ons, and scalable variant/angle generation.

name: AI Creative Design Tools
description: Collection of AI-powered image generation and editing tools that automate creation of marketing assets, thumbnails, product mockups, branding, and visual content for creators and businesses.

name: Generative Brand Studio
description: Tools leveraging multimodal generative AI to automate end-to-end brand creation—logos, color palettes, voice, marketing assets, product mockups, and material variations—from text prompts, sketches, or uploads for rapid, consistent brand production.

name: AI Marketing Creative Tools
description: These tools use generative multimodal AI to convert product images and prompts into production-ready ads, mockups, and multi-platform marketing campaigns with rapid personalization, asset adaptation, and automated creative workflows.

name: AI Comic Generators
description: Tools that convert text, dialogue, journals, or research into multi-panel comics, manga, and webtoons using Gemini/Nano Banana to ensure character consistency, stylistic control, and rapid production.

name: AI Visual Storytelling
description: Tools that use multimodal AI to generate consistent characters, storyboards, comics, and short films from text, images, or prompts, automating visual storytelling, animation, and video production.

name: AI Virtual Try-On

name: AI Photo Transformation
description: Tools that use advanced multimodal AI to generate, edit, and enhance personal photos—producing identity-consistent portraits, stickers, composites, anonymized images, and food visuals for social, professional, and practical use.

name: AI Photo Transformation
description: Projects that use generative multimodal AI to restore, stylize, composite, and personalize photos into art, memories, social assets, and synthetic datasets via natural-language prompts.

name: AI Visual Design Tools

name: Multimodal AI Image Tools

name: AI Interior Design Tools
description: Generative AI tools that transform photos, floor plans, and sketches into photorealistic room, exterior, and 3D visualizations for interior design, virtual staging, remodeling, and shopping.

name: AI Product Visuals
description: AI-driven tools that generate and automate studio-quality product photos, mockups, 3D models, and virtual try-ons for e-commerce, turning single images or prompts into ready-to-use marketing visuals at scale.

name: AI Branding & Ads
description: A collection of multimodal AI tools that automate generation, personalization, and platform-specific adaptation of brand identities, ad creatives, social media visuals, mockups, and end-to-end marketing campaigns.
